<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我家比你想得還整齊，<delay8 />覺得很意外是嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的想法都寫在臉上啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎唷，<delay20 />我忘記用吸塵器打掃家裡了！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />就別在意了吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不准檢查哪裡有灰塵喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00">下次你來的時候，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就讓你嚐嚐我新做的料理吧！<delay frames="30" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼？<delay20 />不必了？</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼樣？這裡就是我的領地唷！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我家……<delay frames="30" />還挺不錯的吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要你想來，<delay20 />
隨時都可以過來玩喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有沒有什麼只想告訴我一個人的事，<delay20 />
或是想找我<delay8 />商量些什麼啊？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在我可以聽你說喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到自己的死黨<delay8 />
都像這樣聚集在我家，<delay20 />
就讓我回想起從前啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡有我、<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
還有<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd01" />啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得這組合很奇妙耶！<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你們居然會有
聚集在我家的一天，<delay20 />
我真是想都沒想到啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然我家<delay20 />注定要變成<delay8 />
大家的聚會場所是嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />能跟死黨玩鬧在一起，
我真的很開心啊！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你們就把這裡當作自己家吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一群人熱熱鬧鬧的<delay8 />果然很開心啊！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最喜歡<delay8 />這種場面啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該怎麼說<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />讓人覺得<delay20 />熱血沸騰？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼大家都到我家來了，<delay20 />
到底是怎麼回事啊？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡可沒有什麼有趣的東西耶<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我家來了好多客人，<delay8 />
真高興啊！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />早知道你們會來的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我肯定會拿出幹勁，<delay8 />
事先準備好派對料理的～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>